            "title": "A股午後升   深股升逾1%  深股一周累升0.84%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股午後大幅向上，滬股轉升，深股升逾1%，兩市成交合計20922.06億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20230629_FI_ASHARE_5_source-ap_.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20230629_FI_ASHARE_5_source-ap_.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指全日升16點或0.41%，報3871，中段低見3850，跌21點或0.54%，為半日低位，隨即反覆向上，午後突破上午高位，升18點或0.46%，為全日高位，全日成交9099.51億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指全日升110點或0.84%，報13258，中段低見13085，跌62點或0.47%，午後大幅揚升，最高報13284，升137點或1.04%，全日成交11822.55億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300全日升28點或0.63%，報4580點 ; 創業板指數收升30點或0.97%，報3194點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指一周累跌13點或0.33%，深成指一周累計升111點或0.84%。</p>\n</div>",
